<div id="fn" class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#TSJN-01-04-0502-fn-0001-ptr" id="TSJN-01-04-0502-fn-0001">1</a><p>Preceding two words crossed out in text, and at foot appears this notation in Archibald Blairs hand: instead of Senatorial districts in the Second line read Counties.</p></div>
